metadata.name: Resilience
metadata.description:
This piece was inspired by The Radoms NFT. They minted in a tough time as the markets were not doing well.

They didn't give up. The fought hard, and sold out despite many obstacles.

This piece is reserved for their community

The first purchase of this NFT comes with the physical sculpture. After that it's in the hands of the holders

Holders can request the 3D file for free use.

Contact OGRE in one of the following ways for shipping coordination.  
Twitter - @OGRE_3D  
Email - Matthewgrote@gmail.com
